Class APICall

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.os.AsyncTask<java.lang.Void,java.lang.Void,java.lang.Void>
      • com.patrickauth.petapp.APICall

  • public class APICall
extends android.os.AsyncTask<java.lang.Void,java.lang.Void,java.lang.Void>
    This class handles API calls to PetPanion. Instances of the APICall are created by passing in the string of the endpoint URL, which will be appended to the base URL of PetPanion.
    Since:
    2020-12-16
    Version:
